{{vgname2|育碧哈利法克斯|en=Ubisoft Halifax}}，前身为'''Longtail Studios'''，是Gérard Guillemot（[[育碧|育碧]]的联合创始人之一）创立的游戏开发工作室。该工作室位于加拿大哈利法克斯。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/ubisoft-acquires-rocksmith-developer-longtail-studios/0157342|title=Ubisoft acquires Rocksmith developer Longtail Studios|first=Alex|last=Calvin|work=MCVUK|date=October 14, 2015|accessdate=October 15, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018231700/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/ubisoft-acquires-rocksmith-developer-longtail-studios/0157342|archivedate=2015年10月18日|df=}}</ref>本工作室于2015年10月被育碧收购。

Longtail Studios在魁北克省的工作室于2010年被育碧收购，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/121988/Ubisoft_Acquires_Longtails_Quebec_Studio.php|title=Ubisoft Acquires Longtail's Quebec Studio|first=Leigh|last=Alexander|date=November 3, 2010|accessdate=October 13, 2015}}</ref>2015年10月14日育碧收购整间工作室，工作室的重点将转移到开发三A级手机游戏。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-10-14-ubisoft-acquires-longtail-studios|title=Ubisoft acquires Longtail Studios|first=Matthew|last=Handrahan|date=October 14, 2015|accessdate=October 15, 2015|work=Gameindustry.biz}}</ref>工作室更名为育碧哈利法克斯。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://venturebeat.com/2015/10/13/ubisoft-adds-another-team-in-canada-as-it-acquires-developer-longtail-halifax/|title=Ubisoft adds another team in Canada as it acquires developer Longtail Halifax|first=Jeff|last=Grubb|work=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]]|date=October 13, 2015|accessdate=October 15, 2015}}</ref>

